title: Taylor Swift is unrecognisable in Vogue
text:
Taylor Swift looks unrecognisable on Vogue Australia cover AAP and staff writers news.com.au Taylor Swift looks unrecognisable on Vogue Australia cover AAP and staff writers news.com.au Taylor Swift looks unrecognisable on Vogue Australia cover. 
YOU might not recognise her, but apparently Taylor Swift is on the cover of Vogue Australia’s November issue. 
Wearing in a blue Schiaparelli haute couture dress, Swift is barely recognisable with straight ‘bronde’ hair and a fringe. 
In the interview with the mag, the 25-year-old talks about the whirlwind tour that’s followed on from the success of her latest album, 1989 . 
She also explains how she’s been pulling in the famous surprise tour guests like Serena Williams, Julia Roberts and Justin Timberlake. 
“I’ll approach them and say: ‘I’ll fly you to a city on the tour, I’ll fly you there and back,’” she says, aware of the difficulty of surprising fans in 2015. Taylor on the cover of Vogue Australia. 
She describes how sound checks are done without speakers switched on, since fans are outside trying to guess who the surprise guest is. Other Stories
